					<p>Did you know that by 2019, 80 percent of online content will be video? </p><p>In this video (see? Entrepreneur.com knows the deal...), Entrepreneur Network partner Ben Angel describes how conversion rates on landing pages featuring videos increases by 80 percent -- and how you need to get in on this avalanche of a trend.</p><p>Click play to learn how to best approach the video process from a guy who's become an expert on the matter. </p><p><em>Watch more videos from <a>Ben Angel on his YouTube channel here</a>. </em></p><p></p><p><a><em>Entrepreneur Network</em></a> <em>is a </em><a><em>premium video network</em></a><em> providing entertainment, education and inspiration from successful entrepreneurs and thought leaders. We provide expertise and opportunities to accelerate brand growth and effectively monetize video and audio content distributed across all digital platforms for the business genre.</em></p><p><em>EN is partnered with hundreds of top </em><a><em>YouTube channels</em></a><em> in the business vertical and provides partners with distribution on </em><a><em>Entrepreneur.com</em></a><em> as well as our apps on </em><a><em>Amazon Fire</em></a><em>, </em><a><em>Roku</em></a><em> and </em><a><em>Apple TV</em></a><em>.</em></p><p></p>				
				
